ActInternational Bridges and Tunnels Act
SubjectProposed alteration of the Thousand Islands International Bridge
PrecisOrder approving the proposed alteration to the Canadian customs facilities at the Lansdowne Port of Entry at the THOUSAND ISLANDS INTERNATIONAL BRIDGE in order to improve border operation efficiency and reduce border wait time for passengers and commercial vehicles travelling to Canada.
